<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Bonafide Certificate</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Times New Roman", Times, serif;
            margin: 40px;
            background-color: #fff;
            color: #000;
        }
        
        .container {
            border: 1px solid #000;
            padding: 30px;
            width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
        }
        
        .header {
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .header img {
            width: 80px;
        }
        
        .header h2 {
            margin: 10px 0 5px;
            font-size: 20px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        .header h3 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .contact-info {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        
        img {
            height: 80px;
        }
        
        .title {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        .content {
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: justify;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .signature {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: right;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .date {
            text-align: right;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        @media print {
            .no-print {
                display: none;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>


    <div class="container">
        <div class="contact-info">
            <div>
                <div>Email: krishnaprasad.mhm@gmail.com</div>
                <div>viceprincipal.ucek@jntuk.edu.in</div>
            </div>
            <div>

                <img src="/assets/logo_main.jpg" alt="University Logo">
            </div>
            <div>
                <div>Phone: Off No: 0884-2300825</div>
                <div>Mobile: 9908837589</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="header">

            <h2>University College of Engineering Kakinada (Autonomous)</h2>
            <h3>Jawaharlal Nehru Technological University Kakinada</h3>
        </div>

        <hr>
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 10px;">
            <div>Lr. No. B1/Acd/CC/2020</div>
            <div>Date:
                <%= new Date(certificate.approvedAt).toLocaleDateString('en-GB') %>
            </div>
        </div>



        <p><strong>Dr. M.H.M. Krishna Prasad,</strong><br> M.Tech, M.I.E., Fellow(I.W.T. of Udine, Italy), Ph.D<br> Professor of Computer Science and Engineering &<br> <b>Vice-Principal</b>
        </p>

        <div class="title">COURSE COMPLETION CERTIFICATE</div>

        <div class="content">
            This is to certify that
            <strong>Mr/Ms. <%= certificate.student.name %>,</strong> bearing Roll No.
            <strong><%= certificate.student.rollNumber %></strong> is a bonafide student of this college and studied
            <%= certificate.student.course%>
                <%= certificate.semester %> Semester (
                    <%= certificate.student.branch %>) during the academic year(s)
                        <strong><%= certificate.academic_years %></strong>. He/She has completed all the formalities for award of
                        <%= certificate.student.course%> degree.
                            <br><br> This certificate is issued on his/her request.
        </div>

        <div class="signature">VICE-PRINCIPAL</div>
    </div>
    <div class="no-print" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px;">
        <button onclick="window.print()" style="padding: 8px 16px; background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; border: none; cursor: pointer; font-size: 14px; border-radius: 4px;">
          Print Certificate
        </button>
    </div>



</body>

</html>